            <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/tasks/t_deploy-rule-set.dita" xtrc="li:2;81:17">Which Suggested rules are being promoted to Required, and
