            <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/tasks/t_deploy-rule-set.dita" xtrc="li:3;83:17">The date the change takes effect</li>
            <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/rule-creator-guide/tasks/t_deploy-rule-set.dita" xtrc="li:4;84:17">How to run the validation locally to check their articles</li>
